hopobject.body: Where's the postbox? clearmeds.org UENF, LLX, OSX and INEA, Rio de Janeiro's stateenvironmental protection agency agree on at least one point:that water in the Quitingute Channel, which gets run-off fromthe port, became brackish, or partly salty, in late 2012,documents in the court case show. The salination began after theworld's largest dredging ship began digging up beach, dunes andmarsh to build 13 kilometers (8 miles) of docks and shipchannels.
